[In the absence of information concerning the number of confirmed
cases of mumps virus infection, it is difficult to assess the
seriousness of this outbreak. However, it is likely that this outbreak
of mumps, as has occurred recently in this age group elsewhere, is
another consequence of the recent decline in uptake of the MMR
vaccine, which has been the cause of the recent upsurge in cases of
measles. Further information is awaited. - Mod.CP]
